Sex Ratio and the Price of Agricultural Crops in China

Demographic and agricultural crop data for individual counties in China.

chinawomen

Format

A data frame with 51766 rows and 9 variables:

admin
integer: unique county identifier
biryr
integer: year of cohort (birth year)
birpop
integer: birth population in a given year
han
numeric
sex
numeric: proportion of males in the birth cohort
teasown
numeric: quantity of tea sown in the county
orch
numeric: quantity of orchard-type crops planted in the county
cashcrop
numeric: quantity of cash crops planted in the county
post
integer: indicator variable for the introduction of price reforms

Details

See QSS Table 7.4.
